        </profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-06-29T04:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-06-29T04:00:00-05:00" n="525" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d525">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.50 Recovery/6–2948: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nanking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-06-29T18:00:00+09:00">June 29, 1948—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 11:18 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1180. Reference your second paragraph, change being made draft including quoted
                    language since RRC<note n="2" xml:id="d525fn2">Rural Reconstruction
                        Commission.</note> agreement negotiation has been suspended in order
                    accelerate bilateral ([refDep]tel 939, June 28<note n="3" xml:id="d525fn3">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_586">p.
                    586</ref>.</note>).</p>
                <pb facs="0625" n="615" xml:id="pg_615"/>
                <p>Reference your third paragraph, Legislative Yuan passed resolution terms
                    foreshadowed Embtel 1128, June 23.<note n="4" xml:id="d525fn4">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_557">p. 557</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p>Embassy requesting Foreign Minister<note n="5" xml:id="d525fn5">Wang
                        Shih-chieh.</note> authorization to sign.</p>
                <p>Embassy will inform prior signature any deviation amended text now in
                    Department’s hands.</p>
                <p>Sent Department, repeated Shanghai 548.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stuart</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
